headline: Zscaler Stock Sees IBD RS Rating Climb To 76
summary: Zscaler stock had its Relative Strength (RS) Rating upgraded from 70 to 76 Monday — a welcome improvement, but still short of the 80 or higher score you look for. This unique rating tracks technical performance by showing how a stock's price action over the last 52 weeks compares to that of the other stocks in our database.
